task.summary:
added /f rules,
has sub commands /f rules add <String> - adds a rule to list /f rules remove <line number> - remove a rule on a line /f rules clear - clears rules /f rules - returns faction rules
Added config entry for default rules Added to FactionsMemory & Faction interface to get rules.
Started on adding /f coleader I think I did all the stuff in role.java, I basically made the admin role co leader, and added a new role on top called Owner. It needs to get a command, and the old admin command needs editing. along with disband needs a perm check edit so only leaders can disband :) I think the f perms gui will need a new entry too. I just wanted to show what I did with the role first, so people approve of it before I go through with it.
